g.text: Memory Layout Optimization for Mark Phase

p.strong: Key Insight: Memory is the Bottleneck

div.p: Modern CPUs are starved for data:

ul.li: RAM can deliver 1 cache line every 200 cycles

div.p: Solution: Allocate objects sequentially and traverse breadth-first.
Result: 3.6x speedup with zero algorithmic changes!
DFS (Random): 18.7 ms BFS (Basic): 7.2 ms BFS (Prefetch): 5.2 ms 3.6x faster!
DFS (Random): 4.8 GB/s BFS (Basic): 1.6 GB/s BFS (Prefetch): 1.2 GB/s 4x less!
Time 0ns: Load Root [Cache MISS] 5ns: Load Child1 [Cache HIT] Same line! 10ns: Load Child2 [Cache HIT] Same line! 15ns: Load Child3 [Cache HIT] Same line!
